Class InterstitialAdActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.content.Context
      • android.content.ContextWrapper
        • android.view.ContextThemeWrapper
          • android.app.Activity
            • com.facebook.ads.AudienceNetworkActivity
              • com.facebook.ads.InterstitialAdActivity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.content.ComponentCallbacks2, android.view.KeyEvent.Callback, android.view.LayoutInflater.Factory, android.view.LayoutInflater.Factory2, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener, android.view.Window.Callback
    Deprecated. 
    as of 4.16 Audience Network SDK, replaced by AudienceNetworkActivity. InterstitialAdActivity was created to support fullscreen Interstitial ads but has since been repurposed for other needs to avoid additional manifest requirements. This class is provided for backwards compatibility only. You should use AudienceNetworkActivity in your manifest.

    @Deprecated
public class InterstitialAdActivity
extends AudienceNetworkActivity
